        <div id="Netflix">
            <div id="DP">
                <h3>Netflix</h3>
            </div>
            <p>Netflix, Inc. is an American pay television over-the-top media service and original programming
                production company. It offers subscription-based video on demand from a library of films and television
                series, 40% of which is Netflix original programming produced in-house.Netflix was founded in 1997 by
                Reed Hastings and Marc Randolph in Scotts Valley, California. Netflix initially both sold and rented
                DVDs by mail, but the sales were eliminated within a year to focus on the DVD rental business.[18][19]
                In 2007, Netflix introduced streaming media/video on demand. The company expanded to Canada in 2010,
                followed by Latin America and the Caribbean.</p>
