        <div id="VootSelect">
            <div id="DP">
                <h3>VootSelect</h3>
            </div>
            <p>Voot is an Indian subscription video on-demand and over-the-top streaming service, owned by Viacom18.
                Launched in March 2016, it is Viacom18's advertising-led video-on-demand platform[3] that is available
                as an app for iOS,[4] KaiOS (JioPhone) and Android[5] users, and a website for desktop consumption. It
                also accessible through Amazon Fire TV, Roku (for Virgin Media and Sling TV subscribers), Apple TV,
                Android TV and Chromecast devices.Voot is available only in India, and hosts over 40,000 hours of video
                content[5] that includes shows from channels like MTV, Nickelodeon and Colors.[3] Content is also
                available in multiple languages like Kannada, Marathi, Bengali, Gujarati, Odia, Malayalam, Telugu and
                Tamil.</p>
